item.title: About Me
item.description: Abhishek Kumar Software Developer Do you remember the output of the first application you ever build, even if you’re not a developer you must have imagined at least once, how a few lines of codes can make an app on your phone do so many things. Well, I always used to wonder these things and when I wrote my first code and witnessed what a few lines of code can do, I knew what I wanted to be.
